2002-01-20  Abel Deuring <a.deuring@satzbau-gmbh.de>
	* sanei/sanei_scsi.c: set timeout value for all operating
	  systems to 1 minute. The timeout value is now derived from
	  the macro SANE_SCSICMD_TIMEOUT.

