  * umax backend bugfixes (new version number: 1.0 build 31):
    man page uses @LIBDIR@ and @CONFIGDIR@,
    calibration fix for Supervista S-12 and compatible scanners
    directory backend:
      umax.c umax-scanner.c umax-scsidef.h
